{
  "stem": "26609.10",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as I went there, I gave it to the sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said, give it to her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They didn't have bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They didn't have food for the children in the hospital-- milk, nothing, nothing, really nothing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know how those children survived at the hospital, because they didn't give them anything, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I gave it to the sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And said she will give it to her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Much, much later, she told me, when she was out of the hospital and she could talk-- because a long time after the hospital, she couldn't talk.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But many years later, even-- when I found her later, after so many years, she said, I put it under my pillow.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And other children got it away from me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They've seen me hiding it under my pillow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took it away from me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some suspected that she's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I went, day after day, day after day, to the hospital to find out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Finally, I think it was about two and a half weeks later, I came.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she sister said to me, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She is not 100%.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we don't keep children longer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She's better.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It won't come back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She's out of danger.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You can take her home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I said, I want to see her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "First, I don't take her now because we were not allowed to travel on trams.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there were no Jews on the streets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before, even, Jews were not allowed to travel in trams.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were no Jews on the streets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How can I carry her such a long way back, and if someone will recognize me on the street?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I said, yes, can she be picked up tomorrow after tomorrow?",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
